	...Should be recommended
	Excessive alcohol intake, Drinking more than 2 units of alcohol 
	Maintaining a healthy body weight is important - BMI 19-25
	A diet rich in calcium, protein, fruits and vegetables 
	To go outdoors, Avoid (not enough exercise)
	Avoid Lack of exercise results in bone (and muscle) loss. 
	High dietary calcium intake
	Avoid frequent falls
	
	...Prescription
		Bisphosphonates (alendronate, risedronate, ibandronate, zoledronic acid)
		Raloxifene and bazedoxifene 
		Teriparatide and abaloparatide
		Denosumab
		Romosozumab
		Menopausal Hormone Therapy (MHT)*
